t;Always the best aspect is to meet other people and share your ideas and experiences and find out that we are still on the same level despite the fact that we are from different parts of the world&quot;\\\",\\\"link\\\":\\\"http://eb3kitlearning/2018/01/29/dr-lukasz-kozera-wroclaw-researchh-centre-eit-116/\\\",\\\"text2\\\":\\\"undefined\\\",\\\"image_url\\\":\\\"http://eb3kitlearning/wp-content/uploads/sites/6/2018/01/Pola-1-300x265.png\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Dr Lukasz Kosera\\\",\\\"subtitle\\\":\\\"Wroclaw Research Centre EIT+, Poland\\\",\\\"social_repeater\\\":\\\"undefined\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"customizer_repeater_56d7ea7f40d66\\\",\\\"shortcode\\\":\\\"undefined\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"&quot;I got to learn so many things, especially with the data, because I knew some few basics then during the training I got to learn way more&quot;\\\",\\\"link\\\":\\\"http://eb3kitlearning/2018/01/29/ms-deborah-boateng-peace-and-love-hospital-340/\\\",\\\"text2\\\":\\\"undefined\\\",\\\"image_url\\\":\\\"http://eb3kitlearning/wp-content/uploads/sites/6/2018/01/Ghan-300x232.png\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Ms Deborah Boateng\\\",\\\"subtitle\\\":\\\"Peace and Love Hospital, Ghana\\\",\\\"social_repeater\\\":\\\"undefined\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"customizer_repeater_56d7ea7f40d76\\\",\\\"shortcode\\\":\\\"undefined\\\"}]\",\n        \"type\": \"theme_mod\",\n        \"user_id\": 4,\n        \"date_modified_gmt\": \"2018-02-01 08:40:16\"\n    },\n    \"hestia::hestia_team_content\": {\n        \"value\": \"[{\\\"icon_value\\\":\\\"fa-twitter\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"B3Africa aims to implement a cooperation framework and technical informatics platform for biobank integration between Africa and Europe. The informatics platform includes a set of open-source informatics tools for biobank and research activities.\\\",\\\"link\\\":\\\"http://www.b3Africa.org\\\",\\\"text2\\\":\\\"undefined\\\",\\\"image_url\\\":\\\"http://eb3kitlearning/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/logoB3Africa-baseline-web-transparent_300