(990, 8, '2018-02-01 08:55:40', '2018-02-01 08:55:40', '{\n    \"hestia::hestia_team_content\": {\n        \"value\": \"[{\\\"icon_value\\\":\\\"fa-twitter\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"B3Africa aims to implement a cooperation framework and technical informatics platform for biobank integration between Africa and Europe. The informatics platform includes a set of open-source informatics tools for biobank and research activities.\\\",\\\"link\\\":\\\"http://www.b3Africa.org\\\",\\\"text2\\\":\\\"undefined\\\",\\\"image_url\\\":\\\"http://eb3kitlearning/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/logoB3Africa-baseline-web-transparent_300x300-1.png\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Bridging Biobanking and Biomedical Research Across Europe and Africa\\\",\\\"subtitle\\\":\\\"B3Africa\\\",\\\"social_repeater\\\":\\\"[{&quot;icon&quot;:&quot;fa-twitter&quot;,&quot;link&quot;:&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;twitter.com&#x2F;hashtag&#x2F;B3Africa?src=hash&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;customizer-repeater-social-repeater-57fb908674e06&quot;},{&quot;icon&quot;:&quot;fa-info-circle&quot;,&quot;link&quot;:&quot;www.b3Africa.org&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;customizer-repeater-social-repeater-5a69c74718137&quot;}]\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"customizer_repeater_56d7ea7f40c56\\\",\\\"shortcode\\\":\\\"undefined\\\"},{\\\"icon_value\\\":\\\"fa-twitter\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"The Biobank and Cohort building Network (BCNet) was established by IARC in 2013 as an opportunity for LMIC members and international partners to jointly address existing challenges in biobanking infrastructure, including ethical, legal and social issues (ELSIs).\\\",\\\"link\\\":\\\"http://bcnet.iarc.fr/\\\",\\\"text2\\\":\\\"undefined\\\",\\\"image_url\\\":\\\"http://eb3kitlearning/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Artboard-1.png\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Low-and Middle-Income Countries (LMIC) Biobank and Cohort Building Network\\\",\\\"subtitle\\\":\\\"BCNet\\\",\\\"social_repeater\\\":\\\"[{&quot;icon&quot;:&quot;fa-twitter&quot;,&quot;link&quot;:&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;twitter.c